---------------------------------------------------------
Yinspire++ - An efficient spiking neural net simulator
---------------------------------------------------------

COPYRIGHT

  Copyright (c) 2007, 2008 by Michael Neumann (mneumann@ntecs.de).
  All rights reserved.

ABOUT

  Yinspire++ is a very fast simulator for spiking neural nets written
  in C++. It's a complete rewrite of an existing simulator called Inspire, 
  which was developed at the University of Karlsruhe. Interfaces for
  Ruby and Matlab exist (see directory ext/).
